      "title": "<span id=\"#29089\" class=\"scroll-m-16 text-3xl font-bold flex items-center\"><h1 class=\"inline !mb-1 scroll-m-16 text-3xl font-bold\">criticise</h1><div class=\"pl-2 flex-1 text-textSecondary text-xl font-serif\">(v.)</div></span>",
      "html": "<p>“<a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of criticize \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/criticize\">criticize</a>”的主要英国英语拼写方式； 有关后缀，请参见“<a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of -ize \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/-ize\">-ize</a>”。相关词汇：“<i class=\"foreign notranslate\">Criticised</i>”和“<i class=\"foreign notranslate\">criticising</i>”。</p>"
